    "en": {
      "title": "To Ranjan Gangarama who was freed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Minister of State Ranjan Ramanayake, who was pardoned by the President, went to Gangarama Temple, Hunupitiya, Colombo after coming out of Welikada Prison.",
        "Seth Patha blessed Ranjan Ramanayake, the Maha Sangha led by Dr. Kirinde Assaji Thero, Gangarama Viharaya Director, who had returned from freedom.",
        "Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa and a group of parliamentarians also attended the event."
      ],
